h2-get-paywall-remote-config-and-present.translation:
## Obtener el Remote Config del paywall y mostrarlo \{#get-paywall-remote-config-and-present-it\}

Para obtener el Remote Config de un paywall, accede a la propiedad `remoteConfig` y extrae los valores que necesites.

```dart showLineNumbers
try {
  final paywall = await Adapty().getPaywall(placementId: "YOUR_PLACEMENT_ID");
  final String? headerText = paywall.remoteConfig?.dictionary?['header_text'] as String?;
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
  // handle the error
} catch (e) {
}
```

